    "Utility functions for Discord.js bot development",
    "Extended Discord events (member connect/disconnect, timeouts, etc.)",
    "Discord UI components and menus",
    "Canvas rendering utilities",
    "Minecraft API integrations",
    "TypeScript-first with comprehensive type definitions"
  ],
